  "text": "Ears were immersed in mRNAlater solution (Applied Biosystems) and kept at оҖІ80В°C, and then homogenized using Tissue Lyser II (QIAGEN) and total mRNA was purified using the Fibrous Mini kit (QIAGEN). After reverse transcription into cDNA using the Reverse Transcription kit (QIAGEN), PCR was performed on a Viia7 RT-PCR detection system (Applied Biosystems). Full-length versus оҒ„tm Il15ra mRNA was assessed using RT-PCR, whereas levels of all other cytokines were determined via quantitative RT-PCR using SYBR Green supermix (QIAGEN). The sequences of specific primers (from Microsynth) were as follows: Il15 forward, 5оҖ№-CATCCATCTCGTGCTACTTGTG-3оҖ№; Il15 reverse, 5оҖ№-GCCTCT-GTTTTAGGGAGACCT-3оҖ№; full-length Il15ra forward, 5оҖ№-ATGGCCT-CGCCGCAG-3оҖ№; full-length Il15ra reverse, 5оҖ№-TTAGGCTCCTGT-GTCTTCATC-3оҖ№; оҒ„tm Il15ra forward, 5оҖ№-ATGGCCTCGCCGCAG-3оҖ№; оҒ„tm Il15ra reverse, 5оҖ№-GGACTTGTGACTGCCTGTCC-3оҖ№; Il17 forward, 5оҖ№-TTGGAGGCAGACACCCACC-3оҖ№; Il17 reverse, 5оҖ№-GATAGCGGTCC-TCATCCGTG-3оҖ№; Il22 forward, 5оҖ№-ATACATCGTCAACCGCACCTTT-3оҖ№; Il22 reverse, 5оҖ№-AGCCGGACATCTGTGTTGTTAT-3оҖ№; Il23p19 forward, 5оҖ№-TATCCAGTGTGAAGATGGTTGTG-3оҖ№; Il23p19 reverse, 5оҖ№-CACTA-AGGGCTCAGTCAGAGTTG-3оҖ№; Tnfa forward, 5оҖ№-TGTAGCCCACGT-CGTAGCAAA-3оҖ№; Tnfa reverse, 5оҖ№-CTGGCACCACTAGTTGGTTGT-3оҖ№. Gene expression was normalized using the ribosomal protein L27 (RPL27) housekeeping gene and data are represented as fold differences by the 2 оҖІоҒ„оҒ„Ct method, with оҒ„Ct = Ct target gene оҖІ Ct Rpl27 , and оҒ„оҒ„Ct = оҒ„Ct induced оҖІ оҒ„Ct reference , as previously published [CITATION_1] .",
